Paper: 13114292
Title: A new approach to the two-dimensional $σ$-model with a topological  charge
Authors: C. Torrero and O. Borisenko and V. Kushnir and B. Allés and A. Papa
Abstract: Based on character decomposition, a dual transformation is introduced leading to two formulations of the theory which should allow for a removal/softening of the sign problem in the original version. Very preliminar numerical results are commented and remaining problems discussed.
